# E-Commerce Microservices Project

This project is built using Spring Boot Microservices architecture.

Technologies Used:
- Spring Boot
- Spring Cloud Gateway
- Eureka Service Registry
- MySQL
- Maven

--------------------------------------------------

PROJECT SERVICES

1. Service Registry (Eureka Server)
Port: 8761

2. API Gateway
Port: 8080

3. Product Service
Port: 8081

4. Order Service
Port: 8082

5. User Service
Port: 8083

--------------------------------------------------

HOW TO RUN PROJECT

Step 1
Start Service Registry

Run:
ServiceRegistryApplication

Open:
http://localhost:8761

--------------------------------------------------

Step 2
Start Product Service

Run:
ProductServiceApplication

Test API:
http://localhost:8081/products

--------------------------------------------------

Step 3
Start Order Service

Run:
OrderServiceApplication

Test API:
http://localhost:8082/orders

--------------------------------------------------

Step 4
Start User Service

Run:
UserServiceApplication

Test API:
http://localhost:8083/users

--------------------------------------------------

Step 5
Start API Gateway

Run:
ApiGatewayApplication

Gateway API Calls

Get Products:
http://localhost:8080/products

Get Orders:
http://localhost:8080/orders

Get Users:
http://localhost:8080/users

--------------------------------------------------

